Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨天不去屋頂 而在樓梯上吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 分別回教室成了彼此的默契
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,藤宮同學 聽說你和桐生是朋友 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有傳言這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 桐生和藤宮是朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,果然那個傳言是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,居然和桐生是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和桐生同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--op--
